data.description: Check out this spacious house that sits across the road from Cherokee Lake in the Hilltop Lake community. Its a truly unique set up there are 2 kitchens and 2 living rooms, an office that has its own door to the outside, a garage, a carport and storage shed.  This house comes with 2 tankless water heater (one is electric and one is gas), 2 ovens (one gas and one electric), new septic, and fiber internet from Brazos Communications.     Community pool, playground, tennis courts, 18 hole golf course, 4 lakes community, and rooms available around this area for larger gatherings and birthday parties, and a great golf course!
